name: Standard Payload
info:
SPOTS Standard Payload (*QSO Payload)

*type - text (spot or qso)
freq - text
*call - text
calllength - number 
*name - text (call)
comment - text
time - number
qthstatus - text (rover,instate,rarestate,prov,blank)
color - text (based on qthstatus)
 - rover - red #FF0000
 - instate - yellow #FFFF00
 - rarestate - blue #0000FF
 - prov - purple #800080
source - text (CL,SK,CH,HA,PO,MO,LO,DI)
 - CL - Cluster Server
 - SK - Skimmer
 - CH - County Hunters
 - HA - Ham Alert
 - PO - POTA
 - MO - CW Fun MO Spotting
 - LO - Local Skimmer (with custom rule)
 - DI - Digital NC7J Skimmer
*zip - number 5 spaces
*state - text
*lat - text (this is lat of general zip code)
*lon - text (this is lon of general zip code)
*mode - text (CW,SSB,PSK31,RTTY,JS8CALL,FT8,FM,other)
*iconColor (mode for spot) - text
 - CW - purple #800080
 - SSB - green #008000
 - PSK31 - blue #0000FF
 - RTTY - red #FF0000
 - JS8CALL - yellow #FFFF00
 - FT8 - black #000000
 - FM - orange #FF8C00
 - other - White #FFFFFF
*band = text (160M,80M,40M,20M,15M,10M,6M,2M,70CM,other)
*iconColor (band for QSO) - text
 - 160M - purple #800080
 - 80M - green #008000
 - 40M - blue #0000FF
 - 20M - red #FF0000
 - 15M - yellow #FFFF00
 - 10M - black #000000
 - 6M - orange #FF8C00
 - 2M - lime #00FF00
 - 70CM - limegreen #32CD32
 - else - White #FFFFFF
*layer - text band + mode (160M CW)
*label - text band + mode (160M CW)


Location for Variable Define
freq - cluster
call - cluster
calllength - cluster
name - map
comment - cluster
qthstatus - DB
source - cluster
zip - DB
state - DB
lat - map
lon - map
mode - DB
band - DB
iconColor - map
layer - map
label - map


QSO Standard Payload

call - text
name - text (call)
zip - number 5 spaces
state - text
lat - number
lon - number
